   <concept id="FAR_31_103" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">31.103</ph> Contracts with commercial organizations.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1940e8" class="- topic/p ">This category includes all contracts and contract modifications for supplies, services, or experimental, developmental, or research work negotiated with organizations other than educational institutions (see <xref href="31.104.dita#FAR_31_104"
                  base="i1086129"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">31.104</xref>), construction and architect-engineer contracts (see <xref href="31.105.dita#FAR_31_105"
                  base="i1086146"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">31.105</xref>), State and local governments (see <xref href="31.107.dita#FAR_31_107"
                  base="i1086200"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">31.107</xref>) and nonprofit organizations (see <xref href="31.108.dita#FAR_31_108"
                  base="i1086212"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">31.108</xref>) on the basis of cost.</p>
         <ol id="d1910e40" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e24">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The cost principles and procedures in <xref href="Subpart_31.2.dita#FAR_Subpart_31_2"
                        base="i1084539"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  31.2</xref> and agency supplements shall be used in pricing negotiated supply, service, experimental, developmental, and research contracts and contract modifications with commercial organizations whenever cost analysis is performed as required by <xref href="15.404-1.dita#FAR_15_404_1"
                        base="i1106135"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15.404-1</xref>(c).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e35">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            In addition, the contracting officer shall incorporate the cost principles and procedures in <xref href="Subpart_31.2.dita#FAR_Subpart_31_2"
                        base="i1084539"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  31.2</xref> and agency supplements by reference in contracts with commercial organizations as the basis for-</p>
               <ol id="d1910e68" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e44">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Determining reimbursable costs under-</p>
                     <ol id="d1910e78" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e50">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
										                    Cost-reimbursement contracts and cost-reimbursement subcontracts under these contracts performed by commercial organizations and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e55">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
										                    The cost-reimbursement portion of time-and-materials contracts except when material is priced on a basis other than at cost (see <xref href="16.601.dita#FAR_16_601"
                                    base="i1103674"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">16.601</xref>(c)(3));</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e63">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Negotiating indirect cost rates (see <xref href="Subpart_42.7.dita#FAR_Subpart_42_7"
                              base="i1075062"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  42.7</xref>);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e71">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                Proposing, negotiating, or determining costs under terminated contracts (see <xref href="49.103.dita#FAR_49_103"
                              base="i1068616"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">49.103</xref> and <xref href="49.113.dita#FAR_49_113"
                              base="i1069003"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">49.113</xref>);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e82">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
								                Price revision of fixed-price incentive contracts (see <xref href="16.204.dita#FAR_16_204"
                              base="i1104985"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.204</xref> and <xref href="16.403.dita#FAR_16_403"
                              base="i1104478"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.403</xref>);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e93">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
								                Price redetermination of price redetermination contracts (see <xref href="16.205.dita#FAR_16_205"
                              base="i1104997"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.205</xref> and <xref href="16.206.dita#FAR_16_206"
                              base="i1105032"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.206</xref>); and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1935e104">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
								                Pricing changes and other contract modifications.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
